She was very angry,

47:19.920 --> 47:22.790
but, yes, she will go home.

47:26.160 --> 47:28.660
Michael...

47:29.370 --> 47:31.180
if she does not hear a word from me,

47:31.220 --> 47:33.400
she will ask questions.

