50:38.170 --> 50:40.320
I can work with this.

50:41.710 --> 50:46.080
I mean, it's not exactly
what we talked about,

50:46.120 --> 50:48.810
but it has possibilities,
even unfinished.

50:48.820 --> 50:52.440
Uh, ventilation at this
point is the main hurdle,

50:52.450 --> 50:54.750
but with a series of fans
and the right equipment,

50:54.780 --> 50:57.280
I am certain that I could
do a rudimentary cook

50:57.290 --> 50:58.520
at the very least.

50:58.530 --> 51:01.660
Not until it is ready.

51:03.240 --> 51:04.390
Oh.

51:04.400 --> 51:07.000
Um, of course.

51:07.730 --> 51:10.730
We only want to do it
if it's done right.

51:10.740 --> 51:15.440
I was just... exploring possibilities.

51:18.480 --> 51:24.760
I am gonna go up and check the...

51:26.150 --> 51:27.590
Okay.

51:38.900 --> 51:40.880
Oh. Hello.

52:21.370 --> 52:22.600
Of course.

52:22.610 --> 52:24.420
That won't be a problem.

52:28.760 --> 52:30.400
Where do you have it?

52:33.490 --> 52:34.940
Okay.

52:34.950 --> 52:36.380
This should do it.

52:36.390 --> 52:38.280
Chuck wrote a good letter, huh?

52:38.360 --> 52:39.920
Chuck wrote a great letter.

52:43.330 --> 52:46.540
It's not just the words,
though, you know?

52:47.570 --> 52:49.440
It's how you read them.

52:58.510 --> 53:01.660
Jimmy, whatever happens in there...

53:02.480 --> 53:04.340
I'm with you.

53:07.980 --> 53:10.340
Mr. McGill, we've
reviewed all the facts,

53:10.350 --> 53:12.120
the same facts as the hearing committee.

53:12.180 --> 53:13.900
We've evaluated their findings.

53:13.920 --> 53:15.820
All that's left is for us to hear

53:15.840 --> 53:16.950
your prepared statement.

53:16.960 --> 53:19.490
So, whenever you're ready.

53:19.500 --> 53:20.860
Thank you, Your Honor.

53:20.920 --> 53:23.320
I-I don't have a prepared statement.

53:23.330 --> 53:27.330
But I do have this.

53:27.340 --> 53:29.760
Um, it's a letter

53:29.980 --> 53:32.430
from my brother, Charles McGill.

53:32.680 --> 53:35.300
He left it to me in his will,

53:35.310 --> 53:39.180
and I received it last
year after he passed.

53:45.660 --> 53:47.610
"Dear Jimmy,

53:47.620 --> 53:49.620
I have left many things unsaid

53:49.630 --> 53:51.920
in our relationship through the years.

53:51.980 --> 53:52.990
Rather than allow

53:53.000 --> 53:55.200
these unspoken thoughts to die with me,

53:55.280 --> 53:57.720
I've chosen to record them here for you.

53:57.730 --> 53:59.330
I hope you will take my words

53:59.340 --> 54:02.000
in the spirit in which
they are intended.

54:07.040 --> 54:08.620
I remember quite clearly

54:08.640 --> 54:10.970
the day you came home from the hospital.

54:10.980 --> 54:14.140
You can't imagine the joy on Mom's face.

54:14.150 --> 54:17.750
I can honestly say I
never saw her happier."

54:32.540 --> 54:35.360
I'm sorry. I can't do this.

54:37.170 --> 54:38.480
I was...

54:39.700 --> 54:42.070
I was just gonna try to...

54:42.080 --> 54:44.020
I was gonna try to move you all

54:44.060 --> 54:46.720
with my brother's eloquent words,

54:46.780 --> 54:48.780
you know, pull on your heartstrings,

54:48.800 --> 54:50.820
but it's not right.

54:50.920 --> 54:53.080
This letter's between me and him,

54:53.290 --> 54:55.620
and it should stay that way.

54:58.440 --> 55:01.639
Listen, my brother, Chuck...

55:01.640 --> 55:04.760
you... you knew him.

55:04.770 --> 55:08.720
He loved me in his own way.

55:08.900 --> 55:10.900
He loved me as a brother.

55:12.570 --> 55:15.000
He did not love me as a lawyer.

55:16.410 --> 55:18.740
Big reason I became a lawyer was Chuck.

55:18.820 --> 55:22.610
He was the most brilliant
man I ever knew.

55:22.620 --> 55:24.610
And an incredible lawyer.

55:24.620 --> 55:25.860
You know?

55:25.940 --> 55:29.800
And, uh, he knew exactly
who he was... exactly.

55:31.130 --> 55:34.600
And all my life, I wanted
to make him proud.

55:35.460 --> 55:40.900
And he was not an easy man
to make proud, you know?

55:40.940 --> 55:44.430
Like climbing Everest without supplies.

55:44.440 --> 55:47.600
If you were one of the lucky
few who reached that peak,

55:47.640 --> 55:50.220
even for a moment, if
you made him proud,

55:50.380 --> 55:53.340
wow, what a feeling.

55:53.400 --> 55:54.440
Whew.

55:54.460 --> 55:56.980
And he let you know it, too.

55:57.160 --> 55:59.960
But if you weren't one
of those people...

56:01.290 --> 56:03.160
he was polite enough,

56:03.240 --> 56:06.020
but he did not suffer fools, you know?

56:06.030 --> 56:10.020
And he could be
judgmental and difficult.

56:10.030 --> 56:12.640
And he knew how to get under your skin.

56:12.740 --> 56:17.160
And... could be a real son of a bitch.

56:18.200 --> 56:21.270
Chuck was the one who
was always right...

56:21.280 --> 56:23.400
always.

56:23.880 --> 56:26.140
And usually he was.

56:26.200 --> 56:27.340
You know?

56:27.350 --> 56:29.170
So, for a guy like me...

56:31.120 --> 56:32.740
I did lousy in school.

56:32.790 --> 56:34.330
I lacked ambition.

56:34.360 --> 56:36.600
I always cut corners. I mean, for me

56:36.720 --> 56:40.840
to live up to the standards
of Charles McGill...

56:45.870 --> 56:48.290
I mean, look at me.

56:48.300 --> 56:50.560
I'll never be as moral as him.

56:50.570 --> 56:52.460
I'll never be as smart.

56:52.470 --> 56:54.460
I'll never be as respected.

56:56.080 --> 57:00.740
I'll never be as good as Chuck.

57:04.220 --> 57:05.910
But I can try.

57:05.920 --> 57:08.680
I can try.

57:08.690 --> 57:13.760
If you decide, and I
get to be a lawyer...

57:16.160 --> 57:18.090
... I'll do everything in my power

57:18.100 --> 57:20.800
to be worthy of the name McGill.

57:23.770 --> 57:26.920
And if you decide I'm not a lawyer...

57:29.940 --> 57:32.400
... doesn't matter.

57:32.410 --> 57:36.610
I'll still try to be the
best man that I can be.

57:41.200 --> 57:43.080
I'm lucky.

57:43.090 --> 57:44.960
I got this letter.

57:45.690 --> 57:48.420
I never had a chance
to write him a letter

57:48.430 --> 57:51.580
and to tell him all the
things that I should have.

57:53.470 --> 57:56.960
And I got to believe that somehow...

57:57.040 --> 57:59.240
... somehow he knows.

58:04.760 --> 58:07.260
Oh, that's...

58:07.280 --> 58:09.200
That'll have to do it for me.

58:09.860 --> 58:11.900
Sorry.

58:12.580 --> 58:14.150
Thank you.

58:23.280 --> 58:25.339
I knew you could do it! I
knew you had it in you.

58:25.340 --> 58:27.380
- That was so great.
- I mean, yes. They...

58:27.390 --> 58:28.800
They have to reinstate you, right?

58:28.820 --> 58:30.890
- They just have to.
- Uh, yeah. Did you see those suckers?

58:30.900 --> 58:32.399
That one asshole was crying.

58:32.400 --> 58:33.559
He had actual tears!

58:33.560 --> 58:35.060
Jesus, Kim!

58:35.070 --> 58:36.820
Listen, I started reading the letter,

58:36.860 --> 58:38.900
and I just knew it wasn't...

58:38.960 --> 58:40.200
I could tell by their faces

58:40.220 --> 58:41.540
it wasn't gonna be enough, right?

58:41.600 --> 58:44.880
So I just went off on
this flow, you know?

58:44.900 --> 58:46.259
I had this energy going through me.

58:46.260 --> 58:48.360
It was like improv or jazz, and then...

58:48.420 --> 58:50.800
boom! I sunk the hook in!

58:51.600 --> 58:54.500
I am so lucky I have this letter.

58:54.580 --> 58:57.180
God, I could see the Matrix, you know?

58:57.190 --> 58:58.480
I was invincible.

58:58.500 --> 59:00.120
I could dodge bullets, baby.

59:00.160 --> 59:01.980
And you were right. You were right.

59:02.000 --> 59:04.100
It was all about Chuck the whole time.

59:04.140 --> 59:06.530
Oh, Mr. McGill, you're still here.

59:06.540 --> 59:07.540
There's some good news.

59:07.550 --> 59:10.330
- Believe me, I already know.
- Oh, good.

59:10.340 --> 59:11.700
Then if you want to come
with me to the office,

59:11.710 --> 59:13.030
there's some paperwork for you to sign.

59:13.040 --> 59:15.400
Absolutely. Let's do this thing.

59:15.420 --> 59:16.680
Oh, and, sweetheart,

59:16.690 --> 59:19.700
I'm gonna need one more form... a DBA...

59:19.800 --> 59:21.510
because I'm not gonna be practicing

59:21.540 --> 59:23.510
under the name McGill, so...

59:23.520 --> 59:24.700
Shouldn't be a problem.

59:24.740 --> 59:26.146
Just down the hall, we
have all the forms.

59:26.170 --> 59:27.840
- Great. Great.
- Wait. Wh... Wait.

59:27.880 --> 59:29.320
Jimmy, Jimmy, what?

59:29.330 --> 59:31.860
S'all good, man.

